{"tid":478894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟護士係唔係咁難做? 值唔值呢個價?","createTime":"2017-11-24T13:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T15:20:22.000Z","uid":137220,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c38ff28bfcc111323df936900a63d36cc7e48c4","tid":478894,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"1.人工值唔值?<br />\n<br />\n如果唔值呢個價...<br />\n就唔會有人出呢個人工，仲要請唔夠人<br />\n<br />\n成日話一出黎三萬，只係講緊公立ja...30k係高<br />\n但私家仲高多幾k，唔通私家仲傻仔過公立?<br />\n<br />\n點解咁&quot;well paid for it?&quot;<br />\n因為供求問題姐...<br />\n<br />\n一方面好多人話，多左好多mk無心做ge入行，點解都fill唔到D空缺?<br />\n因為流失率都高，因為好多人做唔住，頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n如果私家係市場價，公立咪underpaid lo....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.點解呻?<br />\n似乎好多人唔gur ge重點係護士成日呻....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我睇法係社會對護士，甚至係成個醫療都有&quot;唔合理ge期望&quot;...<br />\n而呢種&quot;唔合理ge期望&quot;，係資源極充足ge情況之下，其實係合理ge<br />\n<br />\n例如...<br />\n要求問病情，見醫生。要求醫生用多D時間睇症....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但以病房護士為例..佢就會諗，我陣間仲要派藥，跟治療(eg洗傷口/檢查/安排檢查)<br />\n呢D野點都緊要過同你解釋病情，就會覺得你呢個要求係&quot;唔合理&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，病人/家屬對成個病情/預後/user experience有任何不滿，咪又係屌曬落護士度<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，你可能話你well paid for it<br />\n<br />\n人工低過你ge助理<br />\n工作忙過你ge醫生咪仲慘?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人工低過你ge助理惡撚過你啦...隨時劈炮唔撈，大有人在，人工低嘛...驚乜?<br />\n你唔見病房入面D姐姐D態度一撚定係西?<br />\n<br />\n工作忙過你ge醫生...真係大部分時間忙工作，忙緊工作，9成時間你都見佢唔到啦...<br />\n屌，都屌都唔到去佢到<br />\n<br />\n何況個個病人/家屬見到醫生都收曬皮，醫生講乜你都要聽架啦...right?"},{"pid":"da7777cf81221ad0948d413d72e6196989c49f53","tid":478894,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"唔值<br />\n醫生又唔夠料做<br />\n咪唯有讀d下欄野"},{"pid":"98ed872186161f6a36dc0146de2b49e3ba7eabc4","tid":478894,"uid":2319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔值<br />\n醫生又唔夠料做<br />\n咪唯有讀d下欄野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖則呢科係無醫生咁深入<br />\n但點都唔會係下欄野囉"},{"pid":"6ee28d01dd49e677dca0e358a46fa2ec5049f93f","tid":478894,"uid":137220,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T13:59:19.000Z","msg":"3.不合理期望<br />\n<br />\n再講多DD...<br />\n<br />\n比人屌--&gt;well paid for it<br />\n工作忙--&gt;well paid for it<br />\n<br />\n人工其實唔係好高.....--&gt;你跟本為錢無心做<br />\n<br />\n有心做，做到OT，又忙，又無得去廁所...etc--&gt;乜乜都係咁，但我就gur少少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有D人睇兩睇新聞，就成日屌香港醫療事故，屌D人廢無心做<br />\n個D事故係咪真係事故? 如果係，個頻率係幾多?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實成個中國/香港社會就係自私，而香港果種仲要係無知ge煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a32e7c82ca8165106e211c2f7440ca031101843","tid":478894,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔值<br />\n醫生又唔夠料做<br />\n咪唯有讀d下欄野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打好有point，掌聲"},{"pid":"3246b03f67b7c0d4df3ab486943eb616d7826288","tid":478894,"uid":136252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:00:19.000Z","msg":"值，因為工作量根本唔撚合理"},{"pid":"f67f13db92db81e2574e1de5b5652893192e04a7","tid":478894,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>值，因為工作量根本唔撚合理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留名睇有人秒回你<br />\n做CS/big4/地盤咪仲忙<br />\n<br />\n又唔見人地呻?"},{"pid":"85e82cf938f317f6f1ef8f683ec0873ab99a0db0","tid":478894,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dceac7e829560c6607a2d32765b90656a501212e","tid":478894,"uid":57186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"做乜呢排咁多護士POST"},{"pid":"4c545f6bd7beb5ce530463f1a086b9a0f4968957","tid":478894,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係醫院打雜<br />\n<br />\n比盡兩皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打太慷慨，不如一皮?<br />\n睇下有無人做?"},{"pid":"7d92ce245f3253bc9ad714a7db45bd9eb4c8b962","tid":478894,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做乜呢排咁多護士POST</blockquote><br />\n呢期興"},{"pid":"383594deaa0ac24ebd8e2bce4e80ab15a966e0ab","tid":478894,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本係醫院打雜<br />\n<br />\n比盡兩皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打太慷慨，不如一皮?<br />\n睇下有無人做?</blockquote><br />\n應該免費啦<br />\n執下屎屎尿尿<br />\n幫你打針派藥咋嘛<br />\n果條弱智都識啦<br />\n<br />\n俾返啲屎佢當出糧咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7999f86c4c788b7ab4a59c6dbecc768c5d45eca4","tid":478894,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:13:50.000Z","msg":"樓主個個留言都覆做緊主持？"},{"pid":"4d4cd29a74669c6f843670a170b7b900ae3e321a","tid":478894,"uid":33322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"其實好坦白講，如果你對比外國同香港護士既人工同patient：nurse ratio<br />\n你會發覺香港護士係underpaid左<br />\n講個例子，英國既nurse搵緊around26000gbp／year，講緊22000HKD鬆d一個月，但係人地既ratio係講緊1：4－6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港既nurse搵多人地1萬，但係個ratio多過人地3倍，返夜講緊閒閒地都1：20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋人地係行緊nurse practitioner既模式，nurse有好大既發揮空間同潛力，primary care nurse可以自己prescribe藥同其他home treatment，務求減低入院率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇番香港，唔係無呢樣野，但係始終香港人極崇拜醫生，神化左呢個職業，令到nurse既地位都有好大影響，一句講哂你病想要醫生定護士睇你？<br />\n咁當然你而家叫d nurse出去讀書都無話唔得，但係醫院d野邊個做？<br />\n同埋醫管局根本唔想搞primary nursing，有錢唔請人train人，永遠得把口話密切觀察，年年幾千萬花紅自己高層袋，frontline做到狗咁就送箱橙黎攞景，明明summer＋winter surge就年年都有，死都唔諗下可以點加快入院輪侯時間，專科門診夠贍死排2年先有得睇，我都唔敢同病人講再等幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結：唔係淨係護士難做，係因為有ha呢舊垃圾令到成個醫療行業都好難做！<br />\n<br />\n利申：做左幾年既rn，只會向圍內人呻"},{"pid":"b2820c152f4a451def9734477be0895b271698ea","tid":478894,"uid":100731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"仲有要同啲大粒野，醫生孭鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}